name: Dynatrace-web-reporter
body:
# dynatrace-web-reporter
(early stage)

* Leverages [dynaTrace](https://community.compuwareapm.com) [REST](https://community.compuwareapm.com/community/display/DOCDT61/Server+REST+Interfaces) interfaces for reporting and server management.

* Provides a web frontend to SaaS dynaTrace instance.

* Uses [smartgwt](https://code.google.com/p/smartgwt/) for windowing and datasource management.

* Uses [GWT HighCharts](http://www.moxiegroup.com/moxieapps/gwt-highcharts/) for charting.

Preview :
![Screenshot](https://sites.google.com/site/laurentizac/home/sample.png)

You can test it on [dynatracewebreporter.appspot.com](http://dynatracewebreporter.appspot.com/)
